						               													<description>Pandora's Box is the first in the Mythology Rummy series of strategic tabletop card games. Pandora&amp;rsquo;s Box  starts with simple rules: draw, play, discard. Additional strategy elements add excitement, wrapped in a tapestry of characters and origin stories from Greek Mythology. Players make points from Myths, steal cards from other players, and ultimately win with the most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You do not need to know how to play Rummy or be a scholar in Greek Mythology to play this game. The fun is in the learning! To win, you must employ strategy, as well as luck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Experience the whimsy of the gods, wield the Midas Touch, and exercise the power of Zeus. Play your cards right, and you will open the unpredictable Pandora&amp;rsquo;s Box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
